{"tid":243462,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(有無熟貓既朋友)隻貓今日嘔左七次","createTime":"2017-05-14T16:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T15:29:22.000Z","uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cbf38d93c0691722bcd3ae76e0ad6b7f536ed122","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:08:19.000Z","msg":"我老母今日打電話同我講，隻貓佢今日嘔左七次<br />\n我番到去，睇開間獸醫又閂左門<br />\n念住聽朝即刻帶佢去睇<br />\n但都好擔心，有無巴絲打知咩事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n［慎入］<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/000714_abc75280f7e9b0817db1138399683707.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F000714_abc75280f7e9b0817db1138399683707.jpg&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=0de94c21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/000714_abc75280f7e9b0817db1138399683707.jpg</a><br />\n佢嘔到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f808773bc559bb0daf84d580d3ef208e57a942","tid":243462,"uid":2208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:09:20.000Z","msg":"全香港得一間獸醫先醫到你隻貓？<br />\n睇第二間佢就會死？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d41b1930fc7fb2e7085bbca4fe72239ebe2e3a5","tid":243462,"uid":17760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:10:00.000Z","msg":"好大鑊下喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快d去睇24喇，VSH 聽人講幾好"},{"pid":"bba9d21856dad8137b638c5a4908531b6e889ad8","tid":243462,"uid":98403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"十二生肖無貓㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 快啲睇獸醫"},{"pid":"334c4de2ed3157824daa722ead5df5c8969d03bc","tid":243462,"uid":76463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:13:20.000Z","msg":"食得太飽？"},{"pid":"6101c454826be273416da116a1828c3d8b982395","tid":243462,"uid":97974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:14:58.000Z","msg":"嘔到咁好似好大獲，睇住其他先啦唔拖得！上facebook d貓group問下你住既附近有咩好既診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7199fdf6ef76a2d9d82a78514f5c7dd70cebb1fd","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:15:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全香港得一間獸醫先醫到你隻貓？<br />\n睇第二間佢就會死？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我打左電話比獸醫問，佢話有氣喘同唔點郁先大問題<br />\n我見同佢玩，佢又肯郁<br />\n所以先念住等聽日先睇，因為其他獸醫唔知好唔好<br />\n唔敢亂帶佢去睇"},{"pid":"80077c476061f5546f5135464e1b9ba092286f74","tid":243462,"uid":80015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:15:07.000Z","msg":"換糧"},{"pid":"d983bfc44f4d9f84057617b0eb42beee8766700d","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:15:26.000Z","msg":"好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd0b3bab2697dabd90cd9a7877646199fb199a1","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換糧</blockquote><br />\n但隻糧佢已經食左兩年都無咁嘔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ce38671bf4d22b3821bda3ea93d8385e776600","tid":243462,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:17:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">十二生肖無貓㗎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 快啲睇獸醫</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"5ab0e691bbdd98db22ff577516eec7f7b400e224","tid":243462,"uid":105678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:17:34.000Z","msg":"呢度啲貓撚只會屌你有咩不足，唔會有實質意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0d1b8495d6aca37c03ba5dfcbdefdffa3d16a9","tid":243462,"uid":12879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:17:50.000Z","msg":"我隻貓之前都喺嘔咗幾次 嘔到有血 不過佢喺食錯嘢先會咁 之後食番藥慢慢好番 但樓主快啲帶貓貓去睇24啦 見到都心痛 希望你隻貓會無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd033fd21f755965062bd1d7983bb12bc4863cc","tid":243462,"uid":58618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"有無柯尿"},{"pid":"e94aaf0cfa2fcb715fa65ceeddc5df4904a6c460","tid":243462,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我隻貓之前都喺嘔咗幾次 嘔到有血 不過佢喺食錯嘢先會咁 之後食番藥慢慢好番 但樓主快啲帶貓貓去睇24啦 見到都心痛 希望你隻貓會無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ae49fead415ec494af55b866fbcd46b0ec1e55","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:19:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無柯尿</blockquote><br />\n好似無"},{"pid":"eca9399736c59f52166a9520966c261e3438e43b","tid":243462,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">十二生肖無貓㗎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 快啲睇獸醫</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n屬貓既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45666286a2e26ddd0d004edc968a748ae3fa8c0","tid":243462,"uid":58618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:21:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無柯尿</blockquote><br />\n好似無</blockquote><br />\n咁你要睇下佢有無唔願郁 有無氣喘 啫啫有無腫"},{"pid":"1fc3c93c78cac6e9208c22c3bcfced448bf1eee0","tid":243462,"uid":71224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢度啲貓撚只會屌你有咩不足，唔會有實質意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫佢帶隻貓去睇醫生仲唔夠實質？唔通要冇專業知識嘅人去亂俾意見？"},{"pid":"377711b3c25c54a5ecf86c1d753b1bec52b54135","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有無柯尿</blockquote><br />\n好似無</blockquote><br />\n咁你要睇下佢有無唔願郁 有無氣喘 啫啫有無腫</blockquote><br />\n我岩岩特別聊佢玩，佢都肯撲下跑下<br />\n無氣喘<br />\n同埋佢係囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999033253d65ba4feabd451abf1f41cd6de804af","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:30:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢度啲貓撚只會屌你有咩不足，唔會有實質意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫佢帶隻貓去睇醫生仲唔夠實質？唔通要冇專業知識嘅人去亂俾意見？</blockquote><br />\n絲打，我會帶佢睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但始終對睇開既獸醫會比較有信心<br />\n可惜佢要聽朝10點先開門<br />\n我上網搵左啲上門獸醫電話問過，佢話有氣喘同𠰴一肯郁先要帶佢睇急症<br />\n但我都好擔心，所以想問下各位巴絲<br />\n再決定依家帶佢去睇24好，定等聽朝狗衝落去。<br />\n始終之前睇過旺角間24麥花臣，啲獸醫勁無愛心。<br />\n啲護士又亂開藥"},{"pid":"8a2ec0262446eb3f2e62d323cd9e89d1657c6e6d","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢度啲貓撚只會屌你有咩不足，唔會有實質意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫佢帶隻貓去睇醫生仲唔夠實質？唔通要冇專業知識嘅人去亂俾意見？</blockquote><br />\n絲打，我會帶佢睇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但始終對睇開既獸醫會比較有信心<br />\n可惜佢要聽朝10點先開門<br />\n我上網搵左啲上門獸醫電話問過，佢話有氣喘同<span style=\"color: red;\">唔</span>肯郁先要帶佢睇急症<br />\n但我都好擔心，所以想問下各位巴絲<br />\n再決定依家帶佢去睇24好，定等聽朝狗衝落去。<br />\n始終之前睇過旺角間24麥花臣，啲獸醫勁無愛心。<br />\n啲護士又亂開藥</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1b0d5a2fb17c5ff621ba0357e69ca51e4bcf0902","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/003157_8343034cc6bbde8cfa83d58ebc45a51e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F003157_8343034cc6bbde8cfa83d58ebc45a51e.jpg&h=0084ee9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附上一張佢既生活照，希望多啲人俾啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f13adcedf69afb8d5252e2a29f3f054f29b87a","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:42:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c0b8df18e5d6942489c0e1708d776e4ba6c4c1","tid":243462,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:44:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢度啲貓撚只會屌你有咩不足，唔會有實質意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫佢帶隻貓去睇醫生仲唔夠實質？唔通要冇專業知識嘅人去亂俾意見？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓撚，唔該睇內文，樓主一早講咗原因同聽朝睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你冇專業知識就麻煩收聲等有嘅答，唔係尻屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c063d60ec6f0c1f3810d55a6b960fd21c272a0e","tid":243462,"uid":31278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:56:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢度啲貓撚只會屌你有咩不足，唔會有實質意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫佢帶隻貓去睇醫生仲唔夠實質？唔通要冇專業知識嘅人去亂俾意見？</blockquote><br />\n人地係希望有經驗既人俾到意見<br />\n係人都知要睇醫生<br />\n你當樓主on9定弱智況且人地都講左點解要等聽朝先睇醫生<br />\n吖唔關樓主事 應該係你係盲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a801084ab6be6334d46306766c62d52c0a36f7","tid":243462,"uid":31278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:59:46.000Z","msg":"Btw 樓主你睇下貓貓耳仔有冇熱<br />\n之前試過屋企拖完地隻貓lam地下搞到lam到漂白水嘔到九彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (個陣岩岩養乜都唔識求大家屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n然後獸醫教話摸下耳仔如果好熱即係發燒"},{"pid":"0209361d42248b96f70de2649241a896902184c2","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢度啲貓撚只會屌你有咩不足，唔會有實質意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫佢帶隻貓去睇醫生仲唔夠實質？唔通要冇專業知識嘅人去亂俾意見？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n貓撚，唔該睇內文，樓主一早講咗原因同聽朝睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你冇專業知識就麻煩收聲等有嘅答，唔係尻屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前睇過間24，明明上次開藥有A,B,C藥。下次睇佢開A,B,D藥，然後無講A,B藥重覆，淨係叫我準時喂佢。<br />\n我喂完第一次發覺唔妥先知A,B藥喂左兩次。<br />\n打去間獸醫，個護士仲好串咁反問我:「咁你想點?」"},{"pid":"e91a496d753101c504585f62fa52052993f2085b","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw 樓主你睇下貓貓耳仔有冇熱<br />\n之前試過屋企拖完地隻貓lam地下搞到lam到漂白水嘔到九彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (個陣岩岩養乜都唔識求大家屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n然後獸醫教話摸下耳仔如果好熱即係發燒</blockquote><br />\n耳仔無熱呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0b5ada883e207bf551e5db4023b7ed36a28eca","tid":243462,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"唔好俾野佢食住 半夜仲唔停即帶睇醫生"},{"pid":"7bccfcc8b3d6e2fedb6367ce1d3594e7d01c800f","tid":243462,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:03:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw 樓主你睇下貓貓耳仔有冇熱<br />\n之前試過屋企拖完地隻貓lam地下搞到lam到漂白水嘔到九彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (個陣岩岩養乜都唔識求大家屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n然後獸醫教話摸下耳仔如果好熱即係發燒</blockquote><br />\n上次我個隻又係唔知lam 左咩<br />\n嘔到無野可以嘔<br />\n禁食一晚去睇獸醫乜都check唔到<br />\n然後正常番"},{"pid":"704aa08ae817f58d8d2147524e0c20a9a7381467","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好俾野佢食住 半夜仲唔停即帶睇醫生</blockquote><br />\n佢之前隔1-2個鐘左右嘔一次<br />\n依家訓左就無嘔，仲好似訓得好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/010559_51614e571d858a907bb34cba45d3ac33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F010559_51614e571d858a907bb34cba45d3ac33.jpg&h=434bc2c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1a400a2068c65f20a3979e7b03df805b1dc8338","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:06:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Btw 樓主你睇下貓貓耳仔有冇熱<br />\n之前試過屋企拖完地隻貓lam地下搞到lam到漂白水嘔到九彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (個陣岩岩養乜都唔識求大家屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n然後獸醫教話摸下耳仔如果好熱即係發燒</blockquote><br />\n上次我個隻又係唔知lam 左咩<br />\n嘔到無野可以嘔<br />\n禁食一晚去睇獸醫乜都check唔到<br />\n然後正常番</blockquote><br />\n聽日10點就狗衝落去睇，佢唔可以有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddce70f0791ed3512232e1a431e39b5d25373800","tid":243462,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0