1,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T18:30:35.000Z","msg":"佢突然訓訓下落地嘔<br />\n太擔心，都係撘的士去睇麥花臣check一check係咪重病<br />\n聽日再去睇開個間double check多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97900f4ca090717cb0d5356f860cf4f79ee273ac","tid":243462,"uid":3515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T18:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢突然訓訓下落地嘔<br />\n太擔心，都係撘的士去睇麥花臣check一check係咪重病<br />\n聽日再去睇開個間double check多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知道要落地先嘔代表佢都仲有意識（好似係）<br />\n<br />\n希望你主子冇事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aecc4a73ffb8fd263bb48a6343722b97eec214b","tid":243462,"uid":93402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T19:00:14.000Z","msg":"嘔太多可能會脫水 留意下"},{"pid":"b66ad5965517640c6a5719d8f0caacee524aa256","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T19:06:28.000Z","msg":"撘左成舊水的士，區內幾間都有急症用緊<br />\n有間收我診症都$1000，針藥另計；要留院五千起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40ce882396da08754b49f14160c63d6d4342c35","tid":243462,"uid":31423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T19:45:49.000Z","msg":"一早帶佢去第二間獸醫啦，你驚個醫生劏左佢咩。。你信任相熟嘅醫生咪睇完呢個之後再睇多次囉，冇理由咁樣拖到第二朝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0dbbcec6b984cc02db99e3304eaf42a6e9dcb0","tid":243462,"uid":68988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T19:57:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一早帶佢去第二間獸醫啦，你驚個醫生劏左佢咩。。你信任相熟嘅醫生咪睇完呢個之後再睇多次囉，冇理由咁樣拖到第二朝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56e737490ef7a9ce7ebc4ec98dd19c0684a9c55","tid":243462,"uid":31423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T20:59:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一早帶佢去第二間獸醫啦，你驚個醫生劏左佢咩。。你信任相熟嘅醫生咪睇完呢個之後再睇多次囉，冇理由咁樣拖到第二朝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"c817759253fbf199c7d8b5d7358e46f4c27c2113","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T21:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一早帶佢去第二間獸醫啦，你驚個醫生劏左佢咩。。你信任相熟嘅醫生咪睇完呢個之後再睇多次囉，冇理由咁樣拖到第二朝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n我去左幾間診所都有急症做緊唔接，有一間一千起跳(針藥另計) 留院仲要五千，仲要唔係即刻有得睇，要等1-2個鐘。"},{"pid":"d719fea2660e70a9d954bad860b62b548da5e2d3","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T21:35:12.000Z","msg":"同埋巴打唔知你有無養寵物，依好多獸醫都睇得好hea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係咪對得寵物多麻目左，成間診所啲人一個笑容都無，完全感覺唔到佢地有愛心。好似淨係想快啲睇完，收你錢，然後下個。"},{"pid":"2081d8817b8d3e7bf93e9d0adfc69cd5502903a0","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T21:37:32.000Z","msg":"我依家通宵唔訓陪住佢<br />\n佢1點半同4點半嘔左次，依家係我隔離訓緊教<br />\n我就等緊十點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3863acbbf75f57d8e054a38bd6afe5f065b395d","tid":243462,"uid":63079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T21:39:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我依家通宵唔訓陪住佢<br />\n佢1點半同4點半嘔左次，依家係我隔離訓緊教<br />\n我就等緊十點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果24個d都唔係即有 真係不如等到10點<br />\n希望樓主隻貓冇乜事啦 頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有4個幾鐘<br />\nbetween 樓主睇開個間係邊度?"},{"pid":"ea08ca9795ec8864bdab0e9cb26f0ef8f6202de1","tid":243462,"uid":102289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T22:37:31.000Z","msg":"希望貓貓快啲好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b22c817107d23769fd2ff2d847691571d57120","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T22:46:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我依家通宵唔訓陪住佢<br />\n佢1點半同4點半嘔左次，依家係我隔離訓緊教<br />\n我就等緊十點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果24個d都唔係即有 真係不如等到10點<br />\n希望樓主隻貓冇乜事啦 頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有4個幾鐘<br />\nbetween 樓主睇開個間係邊度?</blockquote><br />\n係荃灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e845759a09aaf9e2dd4544a702b6466d7bf792","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T22:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>希望貓貓快啲好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ae82d3f0243cdfbc4f1d3ed369c14ef445095e","tid":243462,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T00:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我依家通宵唔訓陪住佢<br />\n佢1點半同4點半嘔左次，依家係我隔離訓緊教<br />\n我就等緊十點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果24個d都唔係即有 真係不如等到10點<br />\n希望樓主隻貓冇乜事啦 頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有4個幾鐘<br />\nbetween 樓主睇開個間係邊度?</blockquote><br />\n係荃灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又係 上次貓狂嘔就去左睇活泉 抽晒血個d 剩係因為嘔到脫水 其他無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36b56243aa02e3088e5e42c7a46d516edf59dc5","tid":243462,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T00:41:55.000Z","msg":"我剩係知屙屎有泡就係細菌感染，唔知嘔係咪<br />\n不過係第一次見啲貓嘔泡，重要咁多，睇落都幾大獲下，同埋貓忍耐力好勁，當佢真係唔願郁就好好大獲咖"},{"pid":"a2c6d9a19778982ea0dd5db6ba5d2a4ae03920ff","tid":243462,"uid":116036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T00:43:43.000Z","msg":"會唔會呢排吐毛咋所以乾嘔<br />\n不過嘔到咁會脫水，唔好再喂野比佢食先"},{"pid":"f8988642551e5b420378640f7b5c4d9a8337d909","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我依家通宵唔訓陪住佢<br />\n佢1點半同4點半嘔左次，依家係我隔離訓緊教<br />\n我就等緊十點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果24個d都唔係即有 真係不如等到10點<br />\n希望樓主隻貓冇乜事啦 頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有4個幾鐘<br />\nbetween 樓主睇開個間係邊度?</blockquote><br />\n係荃灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又係 上次貓狂嘔就去左睇活泉 抽晒血個d 剩係因為嘔到脫水 其他無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今朝十點已經狗衝左去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生話要驗血、照x-ray同驗係咪胰臟炎<br />\n依家仲等緊報告<br />\n希望佢無事啦"},{"pid":"391412d10c061d3a1d19eae3fd7e98fe15bc992b","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:50:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我剩係知屙屎有泡就係細菌感染，唔知嘔係咪<br />\n不過係第一次見啲貓嘔泡，重要咁多，睇落都幾大獲下，同埋貓忍耐力好勁，當佢真係唔願郁就好好大獲咖</blockquote><br />\n佢仲肯跑肯郁既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d484c03ab7d0b260b352e81ab5d872150579eb9b","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會呢排吐毛咋所以乾嘔<br />\n不過嘔到咁會脫水，唔好再喂野比佢食先</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁念，所以已經收起左佢啲野食先<br />\n睇完醫生再算"},{"pid":"9e5e55eb9c066b84cae550bb3bdca0a9c119ae2d","tid":243462,"uid":31278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T05:31:16.000Z","msg":"貓貓依家點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee8fceac8ff29181cb29bcd9f373ae49ed87036","tid":243462,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T06:58:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我依家通宵唔訓陪住佢<br />\n佢1點半同4點半嘔左次，依家係我隔離訓緊教<br />\n我就等緊十點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果24個d都唔係即有 真係不如等到10點<br />\n希望樓主隻貓冇乜事啦 頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有4個幾鐘<br />\nbetween 樓主睇開個間係邊度?</blockquote><br />\n係荃灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又係 上次貓狂嘔就去左睇活泉 抽晒血個d 剩係因為嘔到脫水 其他無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今朝十點已經狗衝左去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生話要驗血、照x-ray同驗係咪胰臟炎<br />\n依家仲等緊報告<br />\n希望佢無事啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望無事啦"},{"pid":"8c151ae1a6738e53fac4c2cdd40de802d9a64c1a","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貓貓依家點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩睇完醫生<br />\n驗左全血、驗左胰臟炎、照左X-Ray<br />\n全部都無問題<br />\n應該普通腸胃炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打左止嘔針，埋單成三千五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562b51f01b96b94974b95eb2ef94bac01a83d76b","tid":243462,"uid":20755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:36:05.000Z","msg":"第一 有冇仲繼續食野飲水<br />\n第二 精神ok?有冇玩/定係訓一日？<br />\n第三 嘔既野全部都係咁樣？<br />\n有冇夾住毛/糧/黃膽水？<br />\n第四 嘔呢個情況keep左幾耐？有冇食開吐毛<br />\n<br />\n如果繼續食野玩訓 其實唔大件事<br />\n但 長期咁嘔 唔係好事<br />\n順便問埋食咩糧？<br />\n我屋企都有養貓 希望望到你啦樓豬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/15/153539_e02aade7e1faa5b1e28223b280f0d5cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F15%2F153539_e02aade7e1faa5b1e28223b280f0d5cf.jpg&h=77730c6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ea09a16d0280c056887b3fe37ff4e0beb7b23c6","tid":243462,"uid":104748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T07:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>貓貓依家點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩睇完醫生<br />\n驗左全血、驗左胰臟炎、照左X-Ray<br />\n全部都無問題<br />\n應該普通腸胃炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打左止嘔針，埋單成三千五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食得太飽，食左啲污糟，嘔毛<br />\n不過真係睇左醫生穩陣啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早排潮濕我隻貓又係咁，不過無嘔咁多<br />\n打去問個醫生，佢話每餐俾小啲份糧，飲多啲水，多啲餵屙毛膏佢食就得"},{"pid":"e49a64f8b35b7c5b1d3fddd07b70400e1379cb0e","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:05:10.000Z","msg":"喂佢食野，喂到周圍都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/000420_6e5d98208ec048e25278d01dc237856b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F000420_6e5d98208ec048e25278d01dc237856b.jpg&h=9c2e6183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6940d8b24bcd121e90e9a49c687fe06c3458f3a3","tid":243462,"uid":98049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:41:09.000Z","msg":"依家仲有無事呀"},{"pid":"ae58f122bc2d9b4866b05b8ef785e00ba8b945f7","tid":243462,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喂佢食野，喂到周圍都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/000420_6e5d98208ec048e25278d01dc237856b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F000420_6e5d98208ec048e25278d01dc237856b.jpg&h=9c2e6183&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打隻手同隻奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4863f1603f744e4fd04072b8b8cc88097148376b","tid":243462,"uid":51411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T17:04:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>喂佢食野，喂到周圍都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/000420_6e5d98208ec048e25278d01dc237856b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F000420_6e5d98208ec048e25278d01dc237856b.jpg&h=9c2e6183&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打隻手同隻奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻貓個樣：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9f8e0ed2edc96ae281630b774542623a125887","tid":243462,"uid":24529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:16:56.000Z","msg":"留名學救貓貓"},{"pid":"432a5085097546f70fe93b6feffed43acbd78d80","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:22:06.000Z","msg":"打左止嘔針，暫時無嘔<br />\n但可能醫生叫佢食隻糧佢唔鐘意食，所以搞好耐<br />\n同埋佢唔肯食藥，我又喂唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抓到我損哂，同粒藥都溶埋仲未喂到佢"},{"pid":"16c5f69cc9ea694e90afc6e7e15f8858a07ffa5e","tid":243462,"uid":7229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:32:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打左止嘔針，暫時無嘔<br />\n但可能醫生叫佢食隻糧佢唔鐘意食，所以搞好耐<br />\n同埋佢唔肯食藥，我又喂唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抓到我損哂，同粒藥都溶埋仲未喂到佢</blockquote><br />\n餵藥最好就用餵藥管，隊落佢個口吱入去，不過要好快手<br />\n如果隻藥唔太臭有時溶落罐頭到都會食<br />\n再唔得試下溶落水再用針筒（冇針頭，餵藥水用個d) 直接吱入佢個口"},{"pid":"1a728c8c498d52b184e1dc6af1bec49bbdf5d62e","tid":243462,"uid":10111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T07:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>打左止嘔針，暫時無嘔<br />\n但可能醫生叫佢食隻糧佢唔鐘意食，所以搞好耐<br />\n同埋佢唔肯食藥，我又喂唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抓到我損哂，同粒藥都溶埋仲未喂到佢</blockquote><br />\n餵藥最好就用餵藥管，隊落佢個口吱入去，不過要好快手<br />\n如果隻藥唔太臭有時溶落罐頭到都會食<br />\n再唔得試下溶落水再用針筒（冇針頭，餵藥水用個d) 直接吱入佢個口</blockquote><br />\n我試左兩次用餵藥管唔得，岩岩都將粒藥整成粉再用針筒喂"}]}